status_message:
While E3 is a time to celebrate video games, today's mass shooting in Orlando makes it tough to celebrate anything.  From all of us here at IGN, our hearts and thoughts go out to the victims, their friends and family, and everyone affected by this tragedy.

There is a blood drive happening right now to help the victims. You can go to OneBlood (www.oneblood.org) to schedule a blood donation.

We realize, of course, that video games often depict violence. However, video games also bring people together, and that's what we're here to do this week: we're all coming together to share our love and excitement for this art form -- and for the people we play games with.

So let's come together...
link_name: IGN's Statement on Orlando's Mass Shooting
